Class WorkflowItemRole

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.xmlworkflow.storedcomponents.WorkflowItemRole

  • public class WorkflowItemRole
extends Object
    Represents a workflow assignments database representation. These assignments describe roles and the groups connected to these roles for each collection
    Author:
    Bram De Schouwer (bram.deschouwer at dot com), Kevin Van de Velde (kevin at atmire dot com), Ben Bosman (ben at atmire dot com), Mark Diggory (markd at atmire dot com)
